verses.verse: Praise <WH1984> ye the LORD <WH3050>. Praise <WH1984> ye the LORD <WH3068> from the heavens <WH8064>: praise <WH1984> him in the heights <WH4791>.
Praise <WH1984> ye him, all his angels <WH4397>: praise <WH1984> ye him, all his hosts <WH6635>.
Praise <WH1984> ye him, sun <WH8121> and moon <WH3394>: praise <WH1984> him, all ye stars <WH3556> of light <WH216>.
Praise <WH1984> him, ye heavens <WH8064> of heavens <WH8064>, and ye waters <WH4325> that be above the heavens <WH8064>.
Let them praise <WH1984> the name <WH8034> of the LORD <WH3068>: for he commanded <WH6680>, and they were created <WH1254>.
He hath also stablished <WH5975> them for ever <WH5703> and ever <WH5769>: he hath made <WH5414> a decree <WH2706> which shall not pass <WH5674>.
Praise <WH1984> the LORD <WH3068> from the earth <WH776>, ye dragons <WH8577>, and all deeps <WH8415>:
Fire <WH784>, and hail <WH1259>; snow <WH7950>, and vapour <WH7008>; stormy <WH5591> wind <WH7307> fulfilling <WH6213> his word <WH1697>:
Mountains <WH2022>, and all hills <WH1389>; fruitful <WH6529> trees <WH6086>, and all cedars <WH730>:
Beasts <WH2416>, and all cattle <WH929>; creeping things <WH7431>, and flying <WH3671> fowl <WH6833>:
Kings <WH4428> of the earth <WH776>, and all people <WH3816>; princes <WH8269>, and all judges <WH8199> of the earth <WH776>:
Both young men <WH970>, and maidens <WH1330>; old men <WH2205>, and children <WH5288>:
Let them praise <WH1984> the name <WH8034> of the LORD <WH3068>: for his name <WH8034> alone is excellent <WH7682>; his glory <WH1935> is above the earth <WH776> and heaven <WH8064>.

He also exalteth <WH7311> the horn <WH7161> of his people <WH5971>, the praise <WH8416> of all his saints <WH2623>; even of the children <WH1121> of Israel <WH3478>, a people <WH5971> near <WH7138> unto him. Praise <WH1984> ye the LORD <WH3050>.
